<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Annapurna Base Camp & Mardi Himal Trek</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CDN -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap @5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .info-label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #00574b;
    }
    .itinerary-day {
      border-left: 4px solid #00574b;
      padding-left: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .day-title {
      color: #003d34;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container py-5">

  <!-- Trek Title -->
  <h1 class="mb-4 text-primary">Annapurna Base Camp & Mardi Himal Trek</h1>

  <!-- Info Grid -->
  <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="info-label">Duration:</div>
      <div class="info-value">10 Days</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="info-label">Location:</div>
      <div class="info-value">Annapurna Region, Nepal</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="info-label">Difficulty:</div>
      <div class="info-value">Moderate</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="info-label">Starts / Ends:</div>
      <div class="info-value">Pokhara / Pokhara</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="info-label">Meals:</div>
      <div class="info-value">Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="info-label">Accommodation:</div>
      <div class="info-value">Teahouse Lodges</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="info-label">Best Time:</div>
      <div class="info-value">Spring (March-May), Autumn (September-November)</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Short Description -->
  <div class="mb-5">
    <h3>Description</h3>
    <p>This is a breathtaking trek combining two iconic destinations – Annapurna Base Camp and Mardi Himal. The trail passes through lush rhododendron forests, traditional Gurung villages, and offers stunning views of the Annapurna and Machhapuchhre peaks.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Itinerary -->
  <div class="mb-5">
    <h3>Itinerary</h3>

    <!-- Day 1 -->
    <div class="itinerary-day mb-3 p-3 bg-light rounded shadow-sm">
      <div class="day-title fw-bold">Day 01: Drive from Pokhara to Kimche | Trek to Ghandruk</div>
      <p class="day-desc m-0">
        You begin the ABC and Mardi Himal trek from Pokhara. Depart to Kimche early in the morning in a private taxi taking a scenic 1.5-hour route along the Baglung Highway. You will make your way through villages like Nayapul – the gateway to Annapurna, Birethanti, and Syauli Bazar before finally reaching Kimche.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Day 2 -->
    <div class="itinerary-day mb-3 p-3 bg-light rounded shadow-sm">
      <div class="day-title fw-bold">Day 02: Trek from Ghandruk to Landruk</div>
      <p class="day-desc m-0">
        Today's walk begins after breakfast, passing through beautiful terraced fields and small Gurung villages. You will reach Landruk by lunchtime and enjoy panoramic mountain views including Machhapuchhre (Fishtail).
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Add more days similarly -->
  </div>

</div>

